Title: Tobias' Home Page
Body: Date: Tue, 26 Nov 1996 02:52:05 GMT Server: Apache/1.1.1 Content-type: text/html Content-length: 1897 Last-modified: Sun, 18 Aug 1996 21:17:59 GMT Tobias' Home Page ... to go flashing from one end of the world to the other both in mind and body; to try the manners of different nations; to hear the chimes at midnight; to see sunrise in town and country; to be converted at a revival and to circumnavigate the metaphysics!
